author: Marcus Cho
title: Skrillex Joins From First to Last for First Song “Make War” in 10 Years
text:
From First to Last has just recently made their first reunion in more than a decade, with all their original members returning to their respective roles.
In apparent celebration of the occasion, Sonny Moore otherwise known as Skrillex has made a surprise appearance on their new single “Make War.” As the co-writer and contributing vocal/production talent, Skrillex offers a heavily stylized feel for the track as From First to Last makes a welcome return to their signature sound.
